{
  "stem": "11641.4",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Just if he asked me questions, I answered.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But otherwise-- otherwise I wouldn't.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Even with my own children, it's very hard.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I know how somebody else.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I mean, but I have a good relationship with them, thank God.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Knock wood.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But this is something else.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This is your [INAUDIBLE] inner thought.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's the reason I took when somebody asked me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I talked about Rabbi Mehlman.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And remember I was one in the shul-- one Saturday in the shul.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the rabbi of-- leader of the synagogue had the sermon.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And one of his sermon, he relates that he was in the movie-- he saw a movie, And he says, a very hard movie to see.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But nevertheless, it's sort of duty for every Jew to see it, even if you don't like it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But don't take children with you unless they are at least over 10 years of age or more.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "OK, so I [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He had the sermon.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then he, after-- after the service was over, he had a Kiddush.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so I offhandedly tell him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I says, Rabbi Mehlman, I am one of the Schindler's List.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So he looks at me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Doesn't say nothing, so I just walk away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I mingle with other group.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then he taps me on the shoulder.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He says, did I hear right, what you said?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That you were on the Schindler's List?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I says, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He says, how come you didn't tell me?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I says, Rabbi, how is it proper?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I says, hold it a second!",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I'm on Schindler's List.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I wait, you finish talking.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So about 10 minutes later, he comes to me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "While he was-- I'm still there, he says, you know what I just spoke to?",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
